iring to "wipe out Israel as a nation." Written ~1,000 BCE. The nations listed by their ancient names and their modern equivalents:</p>
        <div style="overflow-x:auto;margin-top:16px">
        <table class="verse-table" style="width:100%">
          <thead><tr><th>Ancient Name (Psalm 83)</th><th>Modern Nation</th><th>Religion Today</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Edom, Moab, Ammon</td><td>Jordan / Palestinian territories</td><td>Muslim majority</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Ishmael</td><td>Arab nations / Saudi Arabia</td><td>Muslim majority</td></tr>
            <tr><td>The Hagrites</td><td>Egypt / Arab peoples</td><td>Muslim majority</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Gebal</td><td>Lebanon (Hezbollah region)</td><td>Muslim majority</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Amalek</td><td>Sinai Peninsula area</td><td>Muslim majority</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Philistia</td><td>Gaza / Palestinian coast</td><td>Muslim majority (Hamas)</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Tyre</td><td>South Lebanon (Hezbollah)</td><td>Muslim majority</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Assyria</td><td>Syria / Iraq (ISIS territory)</td><td>Muslim majority</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        </div>
        <div class="callout" style="margin-top:16px">
          <strong>The extraordinary fact:</strong> Every single nation listed in Psalm 83 as Israel's end-times enemy is today a Muslim-majority nation or territory actively hostile to Israel. This was written 3,000 years before Islam existed. A secular scholar would call this coincidence or retroactive interpretation. A theologian would call this prophecy. Either way — the geographic specificity is unlike anything else in prophetic literature.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CONNECTION 7: 313 vs GIDEON'S 300 -->
    <div style="border:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:40px;overflow:hidden">
      <div style="padding:20px 28px;background:rgba(201,168,76,0.08);border-bottom:2px solid var(--gold);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">
        <div>
          <span style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--gold-dim)">CONNECTION 07</span>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;color:var(--gold);font-size:18px;margin-top:4px">Mahdi's 313 Supporters vs Gideon's 300 — The Small Faithful Remnant Pattern</h3>
        </div>
        <span class="match-badge match-partial" style="font-size:13px;padding:6px 14px">STRENGTH: NOTABLE — NUMERICAL</span>
      </div>
      <div style="padding:24px 28px">
