          <h3 style="font-family:'Cinzel Decorative',serif;color:var(--danger);font-size:18px;margin-top:4px">The Sun Rising from the West — Islam's Most Unusual Sign</h3>
        </div>
        <span class="match-badge match-partial" style="font-size:13px;padding:6px 14px">STRENGTH: INTRIGUING — UNDEREXPLORED</span>
